summary:
As Trade Marketing Specialist, Europe and International Markets, I'm in charge of defining, implementing and executing the local trade marketing plans of our distributors, in cooperation with the Sales team. 
I support the TM Director with appropriate recommendations and relevant actions plans, aiming at enabling the Company to achieve a significative competitive advantage and improve market share and sales.
